{
  "stem": "10397.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And eventually started-- he was in the administration, and the circulation department.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Eventually, he became a newspaper man, writing articles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In-- in-- in the-- in high school, he was known for poems.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He wrote poetry-- poetry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was raised, practically, in our home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't think it's relevant, but his father married the second-- his second wife, didn't like him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was-- so he grew-- he was coming to our home, and my mother was his, you know, food, wash out the shirt.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He wasn't very clean, because his mother-- his-- his stepmother didn't want him around, even.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was a good soccer player, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Anyway, when I came to Prague-- with the diploma, which didn't mean nothing, couldn't make a living, I wrote him a letter.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He lived in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I told him the situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He said, come over to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Come over to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my mother went to a resort, because she had a rheumatism, arthritis.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was by myself, and my father was on a business trip.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there was a truck with eggs parked in front of our-- in the area where we lived.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I came to the chauffeur and asked if I come-- can go with him to Prague.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's about 400 miles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He say, sure, hop in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I closed-- I closed the apartments, took a little suitcase with a few shirts, and I rode straight to-- to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got his address.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- we started-- he came from a-- he was a-- every year, every week, he wanted to get married to another girl, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a soft-hearted guy, very good man, very good boy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so, he was away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I sit on the porch, on the steps for about two hours.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
